  "subject": "Chore: Update RTD config for ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13",
  "commit_message": "Chore: Update RTD config for ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13\n\nUpdate .readthedocs.yaml to use ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13, replacing the deprecated ubuntu-20.04 image and EOL Python 3.8. The ubuntu-20.04 build image will be removed by Read the Docs on June 1, 2026.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: Iae8a9822c36c7d9a296d1ded5504a16293d5ff16\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
